02:40:37.252 --> 02:40:46.742
Shri Mataji: Làm tốt lắm.

1510
02:40:46.742 --> 02:40:54.992
[Vỗ tay] Hay lắm.

1511
02:40:54.992 --> 02:40:55.992
Rất đẹp.

